post.content:
These are the Thursdays of the pickup. Pickup between 6:00pm - 7:30pm in Cafeteria #2 - (near band room).

  • 09-11-14
  • 10-09-14
  • 11-06-14
  • 12-04-14
  • 01-15-15
  • 02-12-15
  • 03-12-15
  • 04-16-15
  • 05-14-15
  • 06-04-15

Orders are due by 11pm CST on the Saturdays preceding the pickup date (ex: Saturday, Sept 6 will be the deadline for the first Market Day orders).
